  "Description": {
    "English": "Partial coordinate data, acquired from a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">freighter</span> shot down by pirate faction <span class=\"name name-special\">The Blight</span>. The chart is signed with a snippet of pirate manifesto:<br><br>\"The galactic tunnels belong to the Blight!\"<br><br>The navigational information is corrupted, but appears to be linked to the data acquired from the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">freighter captain</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "部分坐标数据，从一艘被海盗派系<span class=\"name name-stellar\">“瘟疫”</span>击落的<span class=\"name name-special\">货运飞船</span>上获得。图表上书写着一句海盗宣言：<br><br>“银河隧道属于瘟疫！”<br><br>导航信息已损坏，但似乎与从<span class=\"name name-stellar\">货船船长</span>获得的数据有关。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "部分座標資料，從被海盜陣營<span class=\"name name-special\">「毀滅」</span>擊落的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">貨船</span>上取得。該圖表上簽署了一段海盜宣言：<br><br> 「銀河通道是屬於『毀滅』的！」<br><br>導航資訊已損毀，但似乎和從<span class=\"name name-stellar\">貨船船長</span>身上取得的資料有所關聯。"
  },
